title: VR's Most Realistic FPS Is Getting Even BETTER!
description:
Here's an early look at Gunman Contracts Standalone! A realistic VR FPS coming to Steam in early access next year. In this demo, I show you the Gunman Contracts lobby area along with a stairs contract that looks strikingly similar to the stairs from John Wick 4. 

To learn more, join the Gunman Contracts Discord here;
https://discord.com/invite/FCeD9yHtKv

Let me know if you would like to see Gunman Contracts on Quest 2, Quest 3 and PSVR 2 in the future in the comments below...

Thanks for watching []-)
